brief_summary.textblock:
      1. The safety and tolerability of single-dose of SCB-313 will be evaluated by
           intraperitoneal injection;

        2. The safety and tolerability of repeated-dose of SCB-313 will be evaluated by
           intraperitoneal injection once a day for 3 days, and the maximum tolerated dose (MTD) of
           SCB-313 will be determined;
